More:D'Angelico Premier EXL-1 Hollowbody Electric Guitar (with Gig Bag) A true hollow-body electric guitar with warm and organic resonance, the D'Angelico Premier EXL-1 has a floating mini humbucker for pure tone reproduction. The D'Angelico Premier EXL-1 Hollowbody Electric Guitar. D'Angelico's flagship archtop returns in the Premier Series. Crafted from John D'Angelico's original design, the Premier EXL-1's balanced, organic tone recalls the sound of a classic New York jazz box.
